---
title: Cal Smart Southwest Chorizo Skillet with Charred Corn Wild Rice and Pico de Gallo
description: This glorious Southwest-inspired skillet takes things to the next level with a bed of smoky, charred corn tossed with a wild rice medley and topped with spiced chorizo. Hot peppers offer a mild heat that's tempered by pico de gallo!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poelee-de-chorizo-facon-sud-ouest-32eb70cf.jpg
